; Coverage test for post.cc get_display_account (L309-321).
; Balanced virtual postings are wrapped in [] (L314-315),
; unbalanced virtual postings are wrapped in () (L316-317).
; Non-virtual postings are shown without wrapping.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food         $10.00
    Assets:Cash
    [Savings:Reserve]     $10.00
    [Savings:Reserve2]   -$10.00

2024/01/02 Test2
    (Virtual:Budget)      $30.00
    Expenses:Gas          $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(display_account)|%(virtual)|%(account)\n"
Expenses:Food|false|Expenses:Food
Assets:Cash|false|Assets:Cash
[Savings:Reserve]|true|Savings:Reserve
[Savings:Reserve2]|true|Savings:Reserve2
(Virtual:Budget)|true|Virtual:Budget
Expenses:Gas|false|Expenses:Gas
Assets:Cash|false|Assets:Cash
end test
